ball of fire
Homonym Number:
Word Class: phrase
Sense Number:
Definition:(WW2, N. Africa) ball of fire [So P8: 1941-43: Army in Nth Africa; WF; nf W3.] The Second New Zealand Division.
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
