Date:  11/11/1942
Source:  War Speeches
Author:  CHURCHILL
Vol / Page:  1952 War Speeches 2/357
Edition:
Quote:  For the purpose of turning the breach to fullest account, an entirely new corps, the 10th, was formed, consisting of two British armoured divisions and the New Zealand Division - that `ball of fire' as it was described to me by those who had seen it at work.
